Package org.nlpub.watset.eval

Class Measurer<V,​E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpub.watset.eval.Measurer<V,​E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - node class.
    E - edge class.
    public class Measurer<V,​E>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a clustering algorithm performance evaluator. Given a clustering algorithm provider and a set of graphs, it measures the running time of the clustering algorithm on every input graph. Before recording the measurements, it warms up by running exactly the same operation to leverage the influence of JIT and other VM optimizations.
